  "title": "HR Talent Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop job descriptions, identify qualifications, and devise recruitment strategies with hiring managers</li>\n  <li>Utilize various methods to source and screen candidates, including job boards, social media, and referrals</li>\n  <li>Conduct interviews and assessments to evaluate candidate qualifications and cultural fit</li>\n  <li>Execute business development process, managing stakeholders and business proposals.</li>\n  <li>Devise strategic planning and manage projects deliverables. </li>\n  <li>Foster positive relationships with candidates throughout the recruitment process</li>\n  <li>Maintain HR databases, leave records and employee files</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper documentation and filing procedures</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with hiring managers and HR to manage job offers and onboard new hires</li>\n  <li>Keep hiring managers and HR informed of recruitment status</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Bachelors in any discipline, mentorship will be provided</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to build strong relationships with candidates and hiring managers</li>\n  <li>Strong organizational and time management skills with the ability to manage multiple priorities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants, please Email , and look for</p>\n<p>Jensen Fang Lifa</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 99C4599</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Registration Number: R2197080</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
